-

To this day, this is my most legendary piece, kickstarting my career from nothing! The annoying notification sound, lowering your expectations for what's to come, turning into an angry chord progression of sorts, and detonating into a banger that catches you off guard! I am still in wonder of what exactly allowed this song to reach such heights of success. Many creative decisions came together perfectly to make this song work so well. I am extremely grateful to all of you guys for the support, it came at a dark time in my life when I was seriously doubting pursuing music anymore. Special thanks to Zencha, a former staff member at Discord, who picked my song as a honorable mention in the Discord Hackweek 2019 contest. Without this seemingly small feature, perhaps the YT algorithm could have never detected me  =)

#Exyl #FLUTEGANG
